        public int getResponseCode()
        get reponse code
        Returns:
        An int representing the three digit HTTP Status-Code.
        • 1xx: Informational
        • 2xx: Success
        • 3xx: Redirection
        • 4xx: Client Error
        • 5xx: Server Error
        • -1: http error
